📚 Important Commands
Check IP Address
ip addr

or

ip a
Check Network Interfaces
ip link
Check Routing Table
ip route
Check Hostname
hostname
Check Hostname and IP
hostname -I
Ping Google DNS
ping 8.8.8.8
Ping Google Domain
ping google.com
Check DNS Configuration
cat /etc/resolv.conf
DNS Lookup
nslookup google.com

If unavailable:

sudo apt install dnsutils
Dig Command
dig google.com
Show Listening Ports
ss -tuln
Show Active Connections
ss -ant
Network Statistics
netstat -tulnp

If missing:

sudo apt install net-tools
Test HTTP
curl https://google.com
Download File
wget https://example.com
