🔥 Production Scenario

Problem:

Your Jenkins server cannot download dependencies from the internet.

Troubleshooting steps:

Check IP:
hostname -I
Check routes:
ip route
Test gateway:
ping <gateway-ip>
Test internet:
ping 8.8.8.8
Test DNS:
ping google.com
Verify DNS configuration:
cat /etc/resolv.conf
Check firewall rules if needed.
